::: {#94fc4c27 .cell execution_count=21}
``` {.python .cell-code}
(
    by_country
    .ggplot(aes(x = "donors_mean", y = "country"))
    .geom_errorbarh(
        aes(xmin = "donors_mean - donors_sd", 
            xmax = "donors_mean + donors_sd"),
        height = 0.2
    )
    .geom_point(size = 2)
    .labs(x = "Donor Procurement Rate", y = None)
)
```

